Class Point

java.lang.Object
importedImplementations.NGA_MGRS.mgrs.mil.nga.sf.Geometry
importedImplementations.NGA_MGRS.mgrs.mil.nga.sf.Point
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Point
public class Point extends Geometry
A single location in space. Each point has an X and Y coordinate. A point MAY optionally also have a Z and/or an M value.
Author:
osbornb
